item.title: The End
item.author: shawn.graham@carleton.ca (Dr. Shawn Graham)
item.description: Goals for this week Finish crafting your notebook; I will collate these into a OttawaGLAM Workbench. Write up documentation for your notebook; the ‘notebook reflection’ aka the ‘case study’. Remember to consult the Guidance on Building Your Own Notebook and the Guidance for your Notebook Documentation. TALK about what you’re doing in Discord; ask for help from others or from me. I am happy for you to collaborate on both these tasks; just talk to me so that we can be clear about expectations.
